、代码、链接、类、无序列表、有序列表等）。",[303,343,344],{"id":344},"媒体",[226,346,347],{},"用户可以直接将图片拖放到编辑器中。上传模态框会打开，让您选择目标文件夹。",[226,349,350,351,354,355,358,359,362,363,366],{},"通过键入 ",[237,352,353],{},"/"," 并搜索 ",[237,356,357],{},"Image"," 或 ",[237,360,361],{},"Video","，可以快速插入媒体。模态框会打开，您可以从媒体库（即 Nuxt 应用的 ",[237,364,365],{},"public"," 文件夹）中选择想要插入的媒体。",[226,368,369,370,277],{},"在媒体模态框中，您可以为 SEO 和无障碍目的设置",[241,371,375],{"href":372,"rel":373},"https://www.w3schools.com/tags/att_img_alt.asp",[374],"nofollow","alt 属性",[303,377,379],{"id":378},"vue-组件","Vue 组件",[226,381,382,383,386],{},"此编辑器的卓越功能之一是能够直接在编辑器中集成和自定义任何复杂的 ",[237,384,385],{},"Vue"," 组件。",[388,389,390],"h4",{"id":390},"创建并集成您自己的组件",[226,392,393],{},"开发者可以创建任何视觉复杂的组件，编辑者能够使用它们并专注于内容。编辑者还可以调整组件属性、样式及行为以满足具体需求，只要开发者使其可定制即可。",[395,396,398,401,408,771,780,839,843,852,855,864],"steps",{"level":397},"4",[388,399,400],{"id":400},"创建您的组件",[226,402,403,404,407],{},"您可以创建 Vue 组件并将它们集成到 Markdown 中。只需将组件放置在 ",[237,405,406],{},"/components/content"," 文件夹中即可使用。",[409,410,416],"pre",{"className":411,"code":412,"filename":413,"language":414,"meta":415,"style":415},"language-vue shiki shiki-themes material-theme-lighter material-theme material-theme-palenight","\u003Ctemplate>\n  \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex items-center justify-center border rounded-lg p-1.5\">\n      \u003CUIcon :name=\"icon\" />\n    \u003C/div>\n    \u003Cdiv class=\"flex flex-col\">\n      \u003Ch3 class=\"font-semibold\">\n        \u003CContentSlot name=\"title\" />\n      \u003C/h3>\n      \u003Cspan>\n        \u003CContentSlot name=\"description\" />\n      \u003C/span>\n    \u003C/div>\n  \u003C/div>\n\u003C/template>\n\n\u003Cscript setup lang=\"ts\">\ndefineProps({\n  icon: {\n    type: String,\n    default: 'i-ph-cursor-click',\n  },\n})\n\u003C/script>\n","components/content/HomeFeature.vue","vue","",[237,417,418,434,461,482,506,516,536,556,579,589,598,618,627,636,646,656,663,688,702,714,728,747,753,762],{"__ignoreMap":415},